      "authorAssociation": "MEMBER",
      "body": "I've added a set of epithelium terms for the requested colon regions:\n\n- epithelium of ascending colon (UBERON:7770001)\n- epithelium of transverse colon (UBERON:7770002)\n- epithelium of descending colon (UBERON:7770003)\n- epithelium of sigmoid colon (UBERON:7770004)\n\nEach term has:\n- A definition following the pattern 'An epithelial layer that lines the {gut region}'\n- 'intestinal epithelium' in genus position as requested\n- Appropriate synonyms and relationships\n\nThese changes have been submitted as PR #3541.\n\n@dragon-ai-agent",
