      "body": "@dragon-ai-agent please also add a set of [lamina propria](http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_8600034) terms each defined part of one of the following gut segments:  ascending colon, descending colon, sigmoid colon, transverse colon, stomach, caecum, rectum.  Each should have a textual definition following the pattern: \"The lamina propria that underlies the epithelial lining of the { gut segment }\".  Note, there is no need to duplicate `intersection_of: part_of { gut segment }` as a relationship. ",
